Output docs/assets/cli-help.gif

Require node

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 26
Set Width 1100
Set Height 560
Set Padding 18
Set BorderRadius 10
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Hide
Type "alias tokentrace='node bin/tokentrace.js'"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "tokentrace --help"
Enter
Sleep 3s
